English: Gather [COUNT_REQUIRED] Plant Samples and make your way to the extraction point
Description:
Don't localize Plant Samples. Plant Samples is because they are important mission objectives. They are searchable in the terminals using the same name. The terminals are in English and is not localized in any way.
A short summary of a mission objective. "[COUNT_REQUIRED]" will be replaced by the number of items the player must gather in order to complete the objective; don't alter these characters, just put them in the gramatically correct position in teh sentence.
